data.name: ReadFips
data.value: select top(1) [STATE], COUNTY, LOCATION, STATE_ABBREVIATION, COUNTY_ABBR from CKT_FIPS where (LOCATION = @location) and (COUNTY = @county) and ([STATE] = @state)

data.name: ReadTribunal1
data.value: select top(1) FIP_LOCATION, IDENTIFIER, FIP_COUNTY, FIP_STATE from CKT_TRIBUNAL where IDENTIFIER = @identifier

data.name: ReadTribunal2
